In ''[[Game of Thrones]]'' Morris played the role ofÂ [[The Tickler]]. He was announced in the role on 6 September 2011.<ref>[http://grrm.livejournal.com/236666.html George R.R. Martin's blog]</ref> He joined the cast as a guest star in the [[Season 2|second season]].
